# AGENTS.md

## Stack
- Vue 3 (Composition API, `<script setup>`) + Vite + Bootstrap 5
- LESS for styles (preprocessor with `javascriptEnabled: true`)
- Pinia for state
- No TypeScript

## Dev commands
```sh
npm run dev   # dev server
npm run build # production build
npm run preview
```

## Path aliases
`@` → `src/`, `@assets`, `@styles`, `@components`, `@sections`, `@partials`, `@pages`

## Sections location
Sections live in `src/sections/` and `src/sections/terrazas/`. Each is a self-contained Vue component. No `src/builder/` directory exists.

## LESS global import
`src/styles/main.less` is auto-imported into every `.less` file via `vite.config.js` `additionalData`.

## Props convention
Sections typically receive props from objects with `config`, `header.config`, `header.content`, and `content` keys:
```js
const sectionProps = computed(() => ({
  ...section.config,
  ...section.header?.config,
  ...section.header?.content,
  ...section.content
}))
```

## Rules
- No TypeScript conversion
- No removing props that are in use
- Preserve Bootstrap 5 classes
- No new dependencies
- Run `npm run build` before assuming something works